The '''Netherlands Handball Association''' ({{lang-nl|Nederlands Handbal Verbond}}) ('''NHV''') is the national [[Handball]] association in [[Netherlands]]. NHV organizes team [[handball]] within Dutch and represents the Dutch handball internationally. The Association is a member of the [[International Handball Federation]] (IHF) and [[European Handball Federation]] (EHF).

==Leagues==

===Men's===
* [[Bene-League Handball]] (along with [[Belgium]])
* [[NHV Eredivisie]]
* [[Eerste Divisie (handball)|Eerste Divisie]]
* [[Tweede Divisie (handball)|Tweede Divisie]]
* [[Hoofdkasse (handball)|Hoofdklasse]]

===Women===
* [[Eredivisie (women's handball)|NHV Eredivisie]]
* [[Eerste Divisie (handball)|Eerste Divisie]]
* [[Tweede Divisie (handball)|Tweede Divisie]]
* [[Hoofdkasse (handball)|Hoofdklasse]]

===national cups===
* [[NHV Cup]]
* [[NHV Super Cup|Super Cup]]

